sentence: Today we know that AHR / CYP1-signaling is involved in an amazing array of genetic networks and subcellular processes critical to lifesub production; crosstalk with hypoxia and Hypoxia-inducible factors (HIF) -signaling pathways; transforming growth factor -signaling pathways, as well as growth suppression; tumor initiation; tumor promotion; transgenerational inheritance and epigenetic effects; chromatin remodeling; histone modification; and aging-related and degenerative disease s.
